## Slide 7 — Market

**Talk track**: {{ market_talk_track_with_explicit_bottom_up_walk }}

**Anticipated questions**:
- "How did you size the SAM?"
- "What's your defensible Year-3 capture rate?"

**Backing data**:
- Plant count: NAM 2024 census (BRIEF.md Market; ref `refs/nam-census-2024.pdf`)
- ACV: cohort summary (BRIEF.md Traction; ref `refs/cohort-summary.xlsx`)
- TAM = plant count × ACV
- SAM = TAM × addressable-segment-fraction (with source)
- SOM = Year-3 capture × SAM (with logic for capture rate)

**Drafter notes**: Bottom-up math shown on slide; the talk track walks the multiplication.

